Injustice/ Splattercannon/ Necross:
 
Splattercannon took Injustice and put him under one arm and jumped out the airlock and sped down to the planet.  Necross followed after him and then waited for Darkfate, so they were not too far apart.  Splattercannon flew through the interferance and landed several kilometers away from anything.  He set Injustice down and they waited for Necross and Darkfate to get down here and get to looing for the rogue minions.

airly2000 <airly2002@...> wrote:
DarkFate:

Darkfate followed them and said "GOOD!!! More fun to us!!! "
